{"content": "I need to multiply 264 \u00d7 374 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 264\u2089 = 2\u00d79\u00b2 + 6\u00d79\u00b9 + 4\u00d79\u2070 = 2\u00d781 + 6\u00d79 + 4\u00d71 = 162 + 54 + 4 = 220\u2081\u2080\n- 374\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 7\u00d79\u00b9 + 4\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 7\u00d79 + 4\u00d71 = 243 + 63 + 4 = 310\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 220 \u00d7 310 = 68,200\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 68200 \u00f7 9 = 7577 r 7\n- 7577 \u00f7 9 = 841 r 8\n- 841 \u00f7 9 = 93 r 4\n- 93 \u00f7 9 = 10 r 3\n- 10 \u00f7 9 = 1 r 1\n- 1 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 1\n\nReading from bottom to top: **113487\u2089**\n\n113487", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 342}